EASTERN MEDITERRANEAN SEA.
EGYPT.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY IN PROGRESS UNTIL 10 FEB 11
   BY M/V RAMFORM VALIANT TOWING TEN 8500 METER
   LONG CABLES IN AREA BOUND BY
   32-33N 030-29E, 32-33N 031-40E,
   32-21N 031-40E, 32-02N 031-32E,
   32-02N 030-54E, 32-13N 030-29E,
   32-33N 030-29E.
   SIX MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 11 FEB 11.
